GNU Guile-RPC
=============

This package provides a pure Scheme implementation of XDR and ONC RPC
(respectively RFC 4506 and RFC 1831) for GNU Guile 1.8.


Requirements
------------

  * GNU Guile 1.8.x or later
    http://www.gnu.org/software/guile/guile.html

  * guile-r6rs-libs 0.1 or later
    http://www.fdn.fr/~lcourtes/software/guile/guile-r6rs-libs-0.1.tar.gz
    http://repo.or.cz/w/guile-r6rs-libs.git

  * Guile-Lib (needed to use the XDR Language compiler) 0.1.7 or later
    http://home.gna.org/guile-lib/

    Actually, 0.1.6 will also work, but you'll need the following
    patch for proper error reporting from the compiler:
    https://mail.gna.org/public/guile-lib-dev/2008-03/msg00005.html .


Development
-----------

GNU Guile-RPC is hosted at Savannah and development uses the Git
revision control system (http://git.or.cz/).

The main Git repository is located at:

  http://git.sv.gnu.org/r/guile-rpc.git

To obtain a local copy, just run:

  git-clone http://git.sv.gnu.org/r/guile-rpc.git

Please email <bug-guile-rpc@gnu.org> for bug reports, comments, patches,
etc.


Enjoy!

